Yes, shaman can slow yout pet and you keep it until boss mob is pulled and then shaman cures his slow.  If it ain't charmed, it dies.  That's my motto as far as those elementals go.  Killing it and then waiting for one to pop to use on boss mob is inefficient.  Therefore, I get a shaman to slow it and when boss is pulled, I get him/her to cure slow nad proceed to rip named mob a new one.  Less risk for more reward.</span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
